                  | What are the general restrictions on specials?
              ul
                li
                  | "Specials" do not apply to existing reservations and must be mentioned when making the reservation.
                li
                  | For online reservations, send us an email after booking asking us for the discount.
                li
                  | "Specials" do not apply for holiday time periods unless specifically stated.
                li
                  | The "Specials" can not be combined with any other offer, package, 'Special' or weekly rates.
                li
                  | "Specials" are subject to change and interpretation of the "Specials" are at the discretion of Océano.
            article
